This is a Nuxt 3 project with Tailwind CSS (via @nuxtjs/tailwindcss module).

STYLING RULES:
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes for ALL styling in <template> blocks
- Do NOT use <style scoped> for layout/spacing — use Tailwind classes
- Tailwind is auto-configured via the @nuxtjs/tailwindcss Nuxt module
- Follow mobile-first responsive design (sm:, md:, lg: breakpoints)

IMPORTANT:
- Always run `npm install && npm run dev` to start
- Use Composition API with <script setup lang="ts">
- Never use `nuxt dev` directly — always use `npm run dev`
